Detection Logic

Detect multiple failed authentication attempts from the same IP in a short time window.

Splunk Query
index=linux sourcetype=secure OR sourcetype=syslog "Failed password"
| rex "from (?<src_ip>\d+\.\d+\.\d+\.\d+)"
| stats count by src_ip user host
| where count > 20
| sort -count
What This Detects

SSH brute force

Password spraying

Credential stuffing attempts

